POP a number a###
POP a letter a
POP a end a
OUTPUT "Enter a string to undergo the procedure."
INPUT original
POP a reverse_this a[original]

reversing
POP a reversed a
"reverse it"
POP letter reverse_this [reverse_this]
POP a reversed a[letter][reversed]
GOTO "end reversal" "" [reverse_this]
GOTO "reverse it" a a
"end reversal"
GOTO "end code" [number] ""

"change letters"
GOTO "enough changing" [number] ""
POP temp number [number]
POP letter reversed [reversed]
GOTO "letter=a" [letter] a
GOTO "letter=b" [letter] b
GOTO "letter=c" [letter] c
GOTO "letter=d" [letter] d
GOTO "letter=e" [letter] e
GOTO "letter=f" [letter] f
GOTO "letter=g" [letter] g
